about: We're students of the "Zespół Szkół Łączności im. Obrońców Poczty Polskiej" in Gdansk. We have prepared the website for the competition: "Śladami Obrońców Poczty Polskiej w Gdańsku". The subject of the competition was interesting for us and we wanted to share our knowledge with others, so we decided to take part in it. The project took us 2 weeks in total. Link to source code:
